description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=0/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. Finish is a simple game where the player controls a little black ball while trying to make it to a purple ball. The Player must watch out for the anything object other than the purple ball or else the player will lose a life. Nine Worlds. Ten Levels per World.
